      "review_title": "Paramedic simulation",
      "review_description": "There are 5 scenarios you can choose from. They are really well made. You have a time limit of ~15 minutes to assess your patient, make any treatments, and transfer them to the hospital. Its well made and seems so real. The weird part is that they email your score. I found that so strange, like just show it to me after the simulation. Also they require you to sign up through the game, but then you have to go to your phone to accept your own invite to create an account. Very odd. Otherwise the simulations are good. I wish there were more, I ended up deleting the game after I finished them all. They should make this game more sustainable to users by creating more scenarios",
